title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Proof of Cheeks
description:
Legal disclaimer: We are not financial advisors, just two handsome geniuses who love to podcast. This week, Jimmy and Larry are hitting the street, betting it all on F/W 21 market week, the curse of influence, how far is too far when it comes to securing a bag on IG, nudes, fits pics as art vs. commerce, STONKS, days of brypto past, our best worst excuses ever and much more.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
